 — Use the Digital Crown to play and pause music, to answer, end, and mute yourself on calls, and to control volume and skip between tracks.', 'A SMARTER CASE — Store in an ultra low-power state with the slim Smart Case.', 'LEGAL DISCLAIMERS — This is a summary of the main product features. See “Additional information” to learn more.'], 'category', ARRAY['apple', 'electronics', 'headphone']));
